{"article_id":"yiVUxUny0kkjbdqe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Last week was rough for the GOP .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Senate Republican health care push failed","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"when Sens . John McCain","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"( R-AZ ) ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"Lisa Murkowski","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"( R-AK ) ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"and Susan Collins","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"( R-ME )","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"joined Senate Democrats","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to block the so-called \" skinny repeal. \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Everything was set .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"House Republicans had agreed to bring this legislation to conference ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"instead of passing it ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"should the Senate succeed in getting 51 votes in the very early morning hours last Friday .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"It ended in disaster .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Senate Majority Leader","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"( R-KY )","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"took to the floor","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"when the bill failed ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"he looked forward to hearing ideas from Senate Democrats on health care ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and that we should move on from health care .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The bill is technically not dead ,","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"but for now it ' s not on the agenda .","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"Congress is supposed to be in recess ;","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"the House already adjourned","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"without a plan","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"to tackle the debt ceiling or other budgetary matters .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Yet , the Senate remains in session .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Sen. Joni Ernst","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"( R-IA )","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"has sent a letter to Sen. McConnell ' s office ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"stringently reminding the Kentucky senator","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that the GOP can not simply back away from the repeal and replace pledge .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"The impact","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Obamacare had on Iowa","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"can not be understated .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"The state ' s last Obamacare insurer , Medica , is mulling","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"either pulling out of the market altogether","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"or enacting a 43 percent premium hike .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"So , you can see the predicament here .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Tax reform is another key item on the Trump agenda ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"but Republicans promised to repeal Obamacare for almost a decade .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"After falling short twice this year","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"and to just say","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"it ' s time","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"to move on","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"is not acceptable ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"and it seems like Sen. Ernst knows that .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Republican failure on health care is not an option ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"unless they want to give their conservative base to never vote Republican again .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"They invested money in candidates ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"canvassed neighborhoods ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"conducted phone banks ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and scarified their weekends for these grassroots activities for nearly a decade .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"All","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"they get is a","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"\" well , we tried \" from Congress .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"That ' s political suicide .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Yet ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"as Guy wrote yesterday ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"GOP health care could be making a comeback on the action item list .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":122,"relation":"